    <text id="A7518T">
        <front id="d2">
            <div1 type="summary" id="d3">
                <p>Sibert apologizes for not being in better spirits at their last meeting and urges
                    Evans to pay her a visit some time soon.</p>
            </div1>
        </front>

        <body id="d4">
            <div1 type="letter" id="d5">
                <opener>
                    <dateline>
                        <date value="1867-02-01">Feb 1, /'67</date>
                        <name type="place">Mt. Solon</name>
                    </dateline>
                    <salute>Mr. D.H. Evans,</salute>
                </opener>

                <p>I promised to send you my photo graph this week &amp; for fear you may think
                    me unfaithful by not doing so I write to tell you why I did not I <hi
                        rend="underline">could</hi>
                    <hi rend="underline">not</hi> have one taken this week. I shall not forget my
                    promise. Will you forgive me for being so uninteresting during our drive to
                    Mossy Creek last Sabbath? I felt silent, &amp; sad, &amp; could not
                    arouse my spirits enough to prove how much I really<pb n="2"/>enjoyed the ride
                    &amp; your kindness in taking me to church Well it seems that I am always
                    doing something over which I must grieve with <unclear>regretful</unclear>
                    sorrow after.</p>

                <p>You must come down soon &amp; tell me you sincerely, &amp; willingly
                    forgive me. then I shall be satisfied</p>

                <p>My dear pa is gone again. Home is not home without the love, &amp; cheering
                    presence of a kind, &amp; beloved father. Lula sends love, &amp; a kiss
                    to you she has not been home-sick yet</p>

                <closer>
                    <salute>Truly</salute>
                    <signed>Mollie Sibert</signed>
                </closer>
            </div1>
        </body>
    </text>
